### 6. Magic Number Test — `CalculateTotal_ReturnsCorrectAmount`

Lines 84–86 assert against `247.50m`, `22.28m`, and `269.78m` — where do these numbers come from? A reader must reverse-engineer the pricing logic to understand the expected values.

```csharp
